> **v4.2 è¿ç§»**: A2UI å°†è¿ç§»ä¸º ToolResultCard æ¨¡å¼ï¼Œè¯¦è§ [backend_refactoring_plan_v42.md Â§2.5](./backend_refactoring_plan_v42.md#25-a2ui-è¿ç§»æ–¹æ¡ˆtoolresultcard)

**v4.2 ç›®æ ‡ç»“æ„ï¼ˆToolResultCardï¼‰**:

```typescript
